java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<Number>, Collection<Number>, List<Number>, RandomAccess
public class NumberList
extends ArrayList<Number>

A class for storing primitive wrappers in a List that can easily be converted to an array of the primitive counterparts
